Invocation Name: atlantica radio
des:
Listen to Atlantica Radio on your Alexa device for commercial and subscription-free music from Canada’s East Coast. 

To start, just say "Alexa, play Atlantica Radio" or "Alexa, open Atlantica Radio" to tune in. To find out what song we're playing, just say "Alexa, ask Atlantica Radio what's playing" or "Alexa, ask Atlantica Radio what song is this". You can stop Atlantica Radio at any time by saying "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
